---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Card from "../components/Card.astro";

const meta = {
  title: "Loumarc Signs",
};
---

<Layout meta={meta}>
  <a href="#main" class="sr-only sr-only-focusable">Skip to content</a>
  <Header location="home" />
  <div class="center" data-location="home">
    <div class="cover" data-location="home">
      <h1 class="text-center font-weight-base font-size-6 max-inline-size-full">
        Bringing visibility <br />to your goals
      </h1>
      <img src="/images/demo-sign.jpg" alt="" />
    </div>
  </div>
  <main class="wrapper" role="main" id="main">
    <article class="region flow">
      <div class="switcher">
        <form class="box" name="first-cta" method="POST" data-netlify="true">
          <input
            type="hidden"
            name="subject"
            value="ðŸ¤–: Main CTA from loumarcsigns.com home page"
          />
          <div class="stack">
            <p class="stack step-0">
              <label for="name">Name</label>
              <input type="text" name="name" />
            </p>
            <p class="stack step-0">
              <label for="email">Email</label>
              <input type="email" name="email" />
            </p>
            <p class="stack step-0">
              <label for="phone">Phone</label>
              <input type="tel" name="phone" />
            </p>
            <p class="stack step-0">
              <label for="message">What are you looking to accomplish?</label>
              <textarea name="message"></textarea>
            </p>
            <p>
              <button type="submit">Send</button>
            </p>
          </div>
        </form>
        <h3 class="box flex items-center">
          Achieve the awareness your business deserves
        </h3>
      </div>
    </article>
    <article class="region flow">
      <h2>Products</h2>
      <div class="reel">
        <Card
          url="#"
          imgUrl="/images/demo-sign.jpg"
          alt="Demo sign alt"
          heading="Channel letters"
          excerpt="There are many things to consider when choosing lighted channel letter signs for your business. Reverse illuminated or lighted acrylic face? LED illumination or neon illumination?"
        />
        <Card
          url="#"
          imgUrl="/images/demo-sign.jpg"
          alt="Demo sign alt"
          heading="Channel letters"
          excerpt="There are many things to consider when choosing lighted channel letter signs for your business. Reverse illuminated or lighted acrylic face? LED illumination or neon illumination?"
        />
        <Card
          url="#"
          imgUrl="/images/demo-sign.jpg"
          alt="Demo sign alt"
          heading="Channel letters"
          excerpt="There are many things to consider when choosing lighted channel letter signs for your business. Reverse illuminated or lighted acrylic face? LED illumination or neon illumination?"
        />
        <Card
          url="#"
          imgUrl="/images/demo-sign.jpg"
          alt="Demo sign alt"
          heading="Channel letters"
          excerpt="There are many things to consider when choosing lighted channel letter signs for your business. Reverse illuminated or lighted acrylic face? LED illumination or neon illumination?"
        />
      </div>
    </article>
    <article class="region flow">
      <h2>What to expect</h2>
      <div class="region switcher">
        <div class="flex justify-center items-center">
          <img src="/images/meet.jpg" alt="" />
        </div>
        <div class="flow">
          <h3>Meet</h3>
          <p>
            The first step is a conversation to better understand who you are,
            and what you want to accomplish. We know this is a step towards
            greater success, and we want to ensure we're in alignment along the
            journey! We'll help you generate, and give you an idea of what to
            expect. We're here to serve you, so feel free to follow up with any
            clarifying questions you may have.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="region switcher">
        <div class="flow">
          <h3>Design</h3>
          <p>
            Once we have a clear understanding of your goals, we'll measure and
            collect photographs of your sign location. We'll craft a design that
            meets your qualifications, and brings life to your brand. We are
            tactical about the tools we use to ensure your vision will be
            executed well, and that you'll have the exceptional visibility you
            deserve.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex justify-center items-center">
          <img src="/images/design.jpg" alt="" />
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="region switcher">
        <div class="flex justify-center items-center">
          <img src="/images/demo-sign-build.jpg" alt="" />
        </div>
        <div class="flow">
          <h3>Build</h3>
          <p>
            Once we have all the necessary approvals, our team transforms those
            designs into compelling awareness that will elevate your visibility.
            We're here to remove weight on your shoulders. Throughout the
            process, we'll be reaching out at specific touch points, for
            instance to inform you of zoning approvals, and to let you get more
            time back to focus on your business.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>
    <article class="region flow">
      <h2>Who we are</h2>
      <div class="region flow">
        <div class="region switcher">
          <div class="flow">
            <h3>Eddie Palardy</h3>
            <p>
              Having been a business owner and coupled with his accounting
              background, Eddie understands the needs of businesses. He brought
              his knowledge and experience into the sign industry in 2016.
              Having the need to grow in a more efficient and better established
              environment, he moved to Loumarc Signs early in 2020 and has
              quickly proved his value to our customers.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-center items-center">
            <img src="/images/eddy.jpg" alt="" />
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="region switcher">
          <div class="flex justify-center items-center">
            <img src="/images/25-years.png" alt="" />
          </div>
          <div class="flow">
            <h3>Building high quality signs in New Jersey</h3>
            <p>
              Loumarc Signs has been creating custom signs in NJ and providing
              marketing solutions in Middlesex, Somerset counties & surrounding
              areas since 1994. Find out how Loumarc Signs can help grow your
              brand today. We look forward to helping you create the ultimate
              indoor or outdoor sign in NJ!
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>
  </main>
</Layout>
